WEBVTT

01:53:25.917 --> 01:53:27.617
but Mother started
pounding on him
with her fists...

01:53:27.619 --> 01:53:29.685
screaming,
"Monster, monster!"

01:53:29.687 --> 01:53:31.053
She yelled at me
to go to the raft.

01:53:31.055 --> 01:53:33.189
(SPEAKING TAMIL)

01:53:33.191 --> 01:53:35.491
I thought she
was coming with me,
or I'd never have...
